quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  53,26,Heewii e malaykaaji e nder kammuuji Й—i tefoore majji nafatah huunde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonande mbo O wela O
  53,27,Pellet Й“een Й“e ngoonЙ—inaani laakira hoЙ“e innira malaykaaji inЙ—e rewЙ“e
  53,28,"Woodanaani Й“e ganndal, alah kove ndewata si wonah sikke, pellet sikke nafatah e goonga hay huunde"
  53,29,Й—uurno oon nduntiiЙ—a jikru amen mbo yiЙ—ah si wonah nguurndam aduna
  53,30,"Ko Й—oon ganndal mum en haaЙ—i, pellet ko Alla Й“uri anndude oon majjuЙ—o laawol Makko, ko Kanko kadi Й“uri anndude oon peewЙ—o"
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yoЙ“a Й“een bonnuЙ“e koЙ“e mbonni ko, O yoЙ“a kadi moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e ko moЖҙЖҙi"
  53,32,"Й“en woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e bakkatuuji mawЙ—i Й—in e pankare [Й“e faggitotaako] si wanaa tokoosi Й—in. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaajuЙ—o yaafuyee. Ko Kanko Й“uri anndude on gila O fuЙ—Й—unoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde wonunoЙ—on fuЖҙЖҙannde ka deedi neeniraaЙ“e mon. Wata on mantu ko'e mon; ko Kanko Й“uri anndude gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  53,33,E a tinaali Й—uurniiЙ—o on
  53,34,"hino okka seeЙ—aa, hooti o Й—awa"
  53,35,Kere o jogi ganndal wirniiЙ—i ngal o yiirata
  53,36,Kaa o humpitaaka ko woni kon e Й—eri Muusa Й—in
  53,37,"e [ka Й—eri] Ibraahiima hunnuЙ—o [ahadi yottini]"
  53,38,"wonnde wonkii [woo] ronndotaako doЕӢgal (bakkaatu) wokkii goo"
  53,39,"e wonnde alanaa neЙ—Й—anke, si wonaa ko o golli kon"
  53,40,"e wonnde golle makko Й—en, aray ka yi'ee"
  53,41,refti o yoЙ“iree Й—e njoЙ“di timmundi
  53,42,e wonnde ko ka Joomi maa woni haattirde nden
  53,43,e wonnde ko Kanko woni Weltinoowo Wullina
  53,44,ko Kanko kadi woni Warooro Wuurnita
  53,45,"e wonnde O tagii resindirayЙ—i Й—in Й—iЙ—i : gorel e deyel"
  53,46,immorde e toЙ“Й“ere maniiyu si rufaama
  53,47,e wonnde ko Kanko woodani tagitugol Й—immun
  53,48,e wonnde ko Kanko woni alЙ—inЙ—o e okkЙ—uЙ—o
  53,49,e wonnde ko Kanko woni JeyЙ—o hoodere Si'ira nden
  53,50,e wonnde ko Kanko halki Aadi'en adinooЙ“e
  53,51,"e Samuuda'en, O heddinaano hay e gooto"
  53,52,"Ko non kadi yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en ko adii[Й“e], pellet, Й“en laatino Й“urЙ“e tooГұude e bewde"
  53,53,e yimЙ“e fitaare Й“en (Й“e) O waylitunoo
  53,54,O hippiri Й—e kon ko O hippiri
  53,55,Ko honЙ—um e neemaaji Joomi ma Й—in sikkitotoЙ—aa
  53,56,Awa oo ko jertinoowo jeyaaЙ—o e jertinooЙ“e adinooЙ“e
  53,57,Darngal ngal non Й“adike
  53,58,"DuГұoowo ngal ko woori Allah, alaa"
  53,59,"E ko ndee yewtere [Alqur'aana] haawetoЙ—on"
  53,60,"HiЙ—on jala, on wullataa"
  53,61,Hara ko on welsindiiЙ“e
  53,62,"Koni sujjanee Allah, rewon [Mo]"
  54,1,"Darngal ngal Й“adike, lewru ndun kadi seekike"
  54,2,"Si Й“e yi'ii maande, Й“e Й—uurnoo Й“e wi'a: \"Ko mbilewu jokkondirngu"
  54,3,"ЖҒe fenni, Й“e jokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Hara le huunde kala no mari ГұiiЙ“irde"
  54,4,"GomЙ—ii kumpite arii e maЙ“Й“e, Й—e haЙ—itorЙ—um woni e mun"
  54,5,"[ЖҠum] ko ГұeГұЖҙal yottiingal. Kono jertingol ngol nafaali"
  54,6,Selu Й“e. Г‘alnde noddoowo on noddoyta e huunde aГұiniinde
  54,7,"jaasuЙ“e ndaarЙ—e, hiЙ“e yaltira e genaale Й—en wano kanuuji caratooЙ—i"
  54,8,"heГұaniiЙ“e noddoowo on. HeeferЙ“e Й“en wi'a: \"Ndee ko Гұalaande sattunde"